to even his girlfriend Tamara, Bobo's life is
falling apart. His constant hallucinations   
leave him with no option but to seek psychiat
help.Going through regression hypnosis, a    
terrifying story about his childhood surfaces
involving a sinister power called Daayan who 
not only destroyed his family but also promis
to return to haunt Bobo.He chooses to ignore 
and move on with his life. Just when his care
and love life is at full throttle, enters the
irresistible Lisa Dutt.Bobo is convinced that
she is the daayan. But is she, really? Or is 
just losing his mind?                        



